---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { index } from '../i18n/translations';
---

<Base translations={index}>
  <h1>
    <span class="lang-en">About Me</span>
    <span class="lang-zh">关于我</span>
  </h1>
  <img src="/images/data_science.png" alt="bio-pic" class="img-portrait" />
  <div class="about-bio">
    <p>
      <span class="lang-en">Hi, my name is Yuqi Chen. I am an aspiring data scientist and machine learning engineer studying data science at Northeastern University.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">你好，我叫陈宇琦，是东北大学数据科学专业学生，致力于成为数据科学家与机器学习工程师。</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span class="lang-en">Quantitative data analysis has transformed the world we live in. The realization that the collection of data in all areas is conducive to all kinds of endeavors — from those personal to institutional — has shaped what products are made, how they are priced, how they are marketed, and more. With my degree, I strive to understand and participate in an increasingly data-driven world.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">量化数据分析正在深刻改变我们所处的世界。数据在各个领域的广泛采集，推动着产品开发、定价策略、市场营销等各类活动的演进——无论是个人行为还是机构决策。凭借我的专业背景，我希望深入理解并积极参与这个日益数据驱动的时代。</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span class="lang-en">My technical work spans supervised learning, time series forecasting — with recent projects including an XGBoost-based NCAA bracket prediction model, a SARIMA/Bayesian natural gas storage forecasting system, a NoSQL analyzer of Federal Reserve Meeting Transcripts. I am fluent in Python and proficient in SQL and the data engineering workflows common to tech pipelines.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">我的技术专长涵盖监督学习与时间序列预测，近期项目包括基于 XGBoost 的 NCAA 篮球锦标赛预测模型、SARIMA/贝叶斯天然气储存预测系统，以及联邦储备会议记录的 NoSQL 分析器。我精通 Python，并熟练掌握 SQL 及科技行业常见的数据工程工作流。</span>
    </p>
    <p>
      <span class="lang-en">Outside of my professional endeavors, I enjoy weight training, hiking and skiing, reading, and meeting new people. Tales of Hulan River by Xiao Hong is my favorite book. I am fluent in Chinese and English.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">工作之外，我热爱力量训练、徒步与滑雪，喜欢阅读和结交新朋友。萧红的《呼兰河传》是我最喜爱的书。我中英双语流利。</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <h1 data-key="projects_heading">Personal Projects</h1>

  <div class="project">
    <h2><a href="/projects/fomc-nlp" data-key="proj4_title">Federal Reserve FOMC Transcripts — MongoDB NLP Analysis</a></h2>
    <p class="date" data-key="proj4_date">April 14, 2026</p>
    <p>
      <span class="lang-en">The Federal Reserve's meeting transcripts are a window into the global economy. This project automatically condenses and organizes all 272 FOMC meeting minutes spanning 30+ years, surfacing four recurring economic themes and tracking which one dominated each year. The result can find application as a feature for trading algorithms, or as a quantitative tool for macro-economic research offices.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">美联储会议记录是洞察全球经济的窗口。本项目自动整理了272份跨越30余年的FOMC会议纪要，提炼出四个反复出现的经济主题，并追踪每年的主导主题。成果可用作交易算法的输入特征，或宏观经济研究机构的量化分析工具。</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="project">
    <h2><a href="/projects/eia-forecast" data-key="proj1_title">EIA Natural Gas Storage Forecast (Ongoing)</a></h2>
    <p class="date" data-key="proj1_date">February 14, 2026</p>
    <p>
      <span class="lang-en">Natural gas is the single largest source for electricity generation in many countries. Correctly predicting its storage levels is a crucial task to utility operators, commodity traders, and many more. We built a SARIMA model and a Bayesian regression model to not only make predictions but also allow users to quantify how uncertain the predicted value is.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">天然气是许多国家最大的单一发电来源。准确预测其储存水平对公用事业运营商、大宗商品交易员等至关重要。我们构建了SARIMA模型和贝叶斯回归模型，不仅提供预测值，还能让用户量化预测的不确定性。</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="project">
    <h2><a href="/projects/conv-manager" data-key="proj2_title">C++ Event Reservation System</a></h2>
    <p class="date" data-key="proj2_date">June 25, 2025</p>
    <p>
      <span class="lang-en">A fully functional booking platform which handles registrations, waitlists, cancellations, and automatic refund calculations. Potential use cases include venue event booking such as concerts and sports games.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">一个功能完整的预订平台，支持注册、候补名单、取消预订及自动退款计算。潜在应用场景包括演唱会、体育赛事等场馆活动的票务预订。</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="project">
    <h2><a href="/projects/march-madness" data-key="proj3_title">Kaggle 2025 NCAA Basketball Tournament Prediction</a></h2>
    <p class="date" data-key="proj3_date">February 10, 2025</p>
    <p>
      <span class="lang-en">A model that predicts college basketball playoff tournament results. Provides quantitative analysis of team strength, schedule difficulty, offensive and defensive efficiencies and etc. which can be used in modern sports which have become increasingly data-driven and analytical.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">一个预测大学篮球季后赛结果的模型，对球队实力、赛程难度、攻防效率等进行量化分析，可应用于日益数据化和分析化的现代体育领域。</span>
    </p>
  </div>
</Base>
